Package: targethelpers
Title: Helpers For Scraping Webdata Using Targets Pipelines 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Niels Ole", "Dam", email = "nd@thingsinflow.dk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Miscellaneous helper functions for building pipelines using the 
    Targets/Tarchetypes packages. Currently only a few functions are implemented 
    for converting data frame rows to individual files, syncing changes by 
    updating only modified rows and cleaning up obsolete files. Useful when 
    scraping webdata.
